50|$|Morija Arts & Cultural Festival, {{also known}} as Morija Festival, is an annual event held in Morija, a large village in the Maseru District of Lesotho. This hugely {{successful}} event is coordinated by the Morija Museum & Archives, with support from many groups including, the Royal Family and the <b>Government</b> <b>of</b> <b>Lesotho.</b>|$|E
